testCase.name: ServiceKitError should have default error properties
ServiceKitError should be able to add extra data as context to errors
ServiceKitError when message or status is undefined should have default error properties
ServiceKitError when AXIOS RESPONSE CODE details provided should have default error properties and details
ServiceKitError when AXIOS RESPONSE CODE details provided when code is CERTS ISSUE should have correct status and properties
ServiceKitHttpError should have default error properties

ServiceKitHttpError when code is CERTS ISSUE should have correct status and properties
ServiceKitHttpError when response is not provided should have default error properties and details
ServiceKitCustomHttpError should have default error properties
ServiceKitCustomHttpError should be able to add extra data as context to errors
ServiceKitApplicationError should have default error properties
